# cargo vendor 的源码校验和对字节负责:Windows 上 autocrlf 检出时把 LF 换成 CRLF
# 会直接触发 "the listed checksum of ... has changed"。vendor 一律按原始字节检出。
lesson3-ralph-loop/examples/rustwrap/seed/vendor/** -text
lesson3-ralph-loop/examples/rustwrap/seed/Cargo.lock -text

# shell 脚本在 Git Bash 下必须是 LF(CRLF 会报 $'\r': command not found)
*.sh text eol=lf
